p: The ClueGO database connects the GO database to Cytoscape, which is an important plug-in for the Cytoscape visual analysis software. ClueGO analysis technology enables the use of similar descriptors for the function of target products from different databases and then classifies and analyzes the targets from biological processes, molecular functions, and cellular components, as well as the enrichment analysis of KEGG pathway (Pâ‰¤0.05), to predict the mechanism of Compound Anshen essential oil in the treatment of insomnia.
